<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied - Rise</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/assets/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/assets/favicon-32x32.png">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #111111;
            --panel: #141414;
            --line: #3a3a3a;
            --text: #ececec;
            --muted: #b8b8b8;
            --error: #ff6b6b;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", ui-monospace, monospace;
            color: var(--text);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, #202020 0%, #101010 40%), var(--bg);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 36rem;
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
            background-color: currentColor;
            mask-size: contain;
            mask-repeat: no-repeat;
            mask-position: center;
            -webkit-mask-size: contain;
            -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
            -webkit-mask-position: center;
            mask-image: url(/assets/logo.svg);
            -webkit-mask-image: url(/assets/logo.svg);
        }
        .state-error { color: var(--error); font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        h2 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--error); }
        p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }
        .user-email {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding: 0.75rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: var(--text);
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .help-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="logo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="state-error">[!]</div>
        <h2>Platform Access Denied</h2>

        <p>
            Your account is not authorized to access Rise platform features.
        </p>

        <p>
            You can authenticate to access deployed applications, but you cannot use
            the Rise Dashboard, CLI, or API.
        </p>

        <div class="user-email">{{ user_email }}</div>

        <p class="help-text">
            If you believe this is an error, please contact your administrator.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
